ZH: 这个人的品德非常高尚。
EN: This person's moral character is very noble.

ZH: 她的品德受到了大家的赞赏。
EN: Her morals are admired by everyone.

ZH: 一个人的品德可以决定他的未来。
EN: A person's morals can determine their future.

ZH: 这个社会需要更多注重品德的人。
EN: This society needs more people who focus on morals.

ZH: 在做事情的时候要时刻保持良好品德。
EN: Always maintain good morals when doing things.

ZH: 品德高尚的人令人尊敬。
EN: People with noble morals are respected.

ZH: 品德是一个人最宝贵的财富。
EN: Morals are a person's most valuable asset.

ZH: 秉公持正是维护品德的重要方式。
EN: Upholding justice is an important way to maintain morals.

ZH: 一个人的品德会反映在他的行为上。
EN: A person's morals will be reflected in their actions.

ZH: 学校应该教育学生培养良好的品德。
EN: Schools should educate students to cultivate good morals.

ZH: 一个人的品德会影响周围的人。
EN: A person's morals will affect those around them.

ZH: 品德优良的人往往能获得更多支持。
EN: People with good morals often receive more support.

ZH: 谦虚是一个人的品德之美。
EN: Humility is a beauty of a person's morals.

ZH: 品德是一个人内在的力量。
EN: Morals are the inner strength of a person.

ZH: 品德高尚的人会受到更多的尊重。
EN: People with noble morals will receive more respect.

ZH: 在困难面前能够坚守品德很重要。
EN: It is important to maintain morals in the face of adversity.

ZH: 意志坚定是品德的重要表现。
EN: Determination is an important manifestation of morals.

ZH: 不轻言放弃是一个人品德的体现。
EN: Not giving up easily is a reflection of a person's morals.

ZH: 家庭是培养孩子品德的第一所学校。
EN: The family is the first school to cultivate children's morals.

ZH: 品德高尚的人能够引领他人向善。
EN: People with noble morals can lead others towards goodness.
